  "prompt": "Which is the best department T-Shirt design in IIT Madras?",
  "response": "The \"best\" department T-shirt design at IIT Madras is subjective and can vary greatly depending on personal preferences, artistic tastes, and the specific departments involved. Each department often has its unique designs that reflect their culture, values, and humor. \n\nCommonly appreciated designs may include clever puns related to the field of study, creative illustrations that symbolize the department, or themes that celebrate achievements and camaraderie among students. Popular departments like Computer Science, Electrical Engineering, Chemical Engineering, and Mechanical Engineering often have dynamic designs that resonate with students.\n\nIf you\u2019re interested in a specific design or want to vote for the best, it might be helpful to check out social media groups, student forums, or events like the annual Tech Fest where these designs are showcased. Engaging with the student community can provide insight into which T-shirts are currently favored!",
